<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 40px; }
        .card { max-width: 600px; background: white; border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #18181b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; }
        h1 { color: #18181b; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        p { color: #52525b; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; }
        .btn { display: block; background: #6366f1; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .footer { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #a1a1aa; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .warning { font-size: 13px; color: #f43f5e; margin-top: 24px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="logo">PrepUp CBT</div>
        <h1>Identity Verification Required</h1>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Your PrepUp CBT account has been successfully initialized. To activate your access and begin your scholarly journey, please verify your email address below.</p>
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="btn">Verify Account Identity 🛡️</a>
        <p class="warning">Note: This verification link expires in 24 hours.</p>
        <div class="footer">PrepUp CBT • Global Verification Engine • © 2026</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
